MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut in the DG12 postcode area of Annan. It has been necessary for our engineers to carry out an emergency shutdown at 2:50pm due to grounded overhead power lines and this may affect the supply to your property. We will work to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 5:45pm. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 2:59pm on Saturday, 31 October 2020
